{
	"Description": {
		"Id": "bd_event_co_byeTurtrus",
		"Name": "Family Matters",
		"Details": "You're in your cabin one evening when there's a knock at your door. Opening it up, you find [[SCN_MW,Sam Marlow]] standing there looking a bit sheepish. \"Commander, I need your permission to leave the company for awhile. My mother is extremely ill and she's asked me to come be by her side. The docs say it's the end and I really need to be there for her. I know you need me here but I can't leave her alone. I'm going no matter what you say but wanted to ask if you'd keep a berth for me when... you know, for when it's over and I can come back.\" You can see the stress in his eyes, this has been eating at him for awhile.",
		"Icon": "uixTxrSpot_MedBayPatient.png"
	},
