			"ResultSets": [
				{
					"Description": {
						"Id": "outcome_0_0",
						"Name": "Pay His Way",
						"Details": "You put your hand on his shoulder. \"[[SCN_MW,{SCN_MW.Callsign}]], you're one of my pilots and that means you're part of the family here. Not only will I keep a seat open for you but I'll help cover her medical costs for you. Go, be with your mother in her time of need.\" His eyes go wide and he sputters for a moment before finding his voice again. \"Commander, I... I'll never forget this, I swear I won't. I'll be back, I promise I will be, and I'll be here as long as you'll have me.\" Turtrus might be unavailable for awhile but you know you just bought yourself a MechWarrior for life and that's worth any price.",
